column5: A few weeks back at the toronto fishing and boat show i signed up for the outdoor canada magazine. Well aparently there was some kind of draw with each supscrption and well i won. Nothing really big like a trip or anything but they callled me today and said i won a new pole and reel, some line, some bluefox and rappala lures. This is big news for me anyway because i never win anything.
Cool.  It's a good magazine.  I get that and OOD and I'm good.  I got a free pocket knife when I subscribed... and it isn't even sharp.    Right on.
congrates .....i cant even win a coffee from Timmies
If you sign up for a OFHA you get a suscrription to OOD and you get a bunch of goodies thrown into the mix..great deal IMO
yup its a good deal i got my delivered last week
In stead of it saying play again ,it should say pay again !! lol
nothing like winning a draw... can no longer say "i never win!"
